name: Catrina / Mexican Skull MakeUp (Dia de muertos) by YeiyeiArt
description:
“It’s the first time I’ve made a Concept and I’m very satisfied with the final result. I think this particular model is very entertaining and may be interesting for some people. Basically it’s the popular makeup (catrina) of the Mexican tradition of the Day of the Dead. It can be used to paint your favorite characters or simply to generate concepts and charming girls in any type of model. The Lora works with a force of (1.0 - 0.5) so it is quite flexible. Use the words (CatrinaMakeUp) to invoke the Lora and obtain greater precision, it can also help to put (Makeup by CatrinaMakeUp). Remember to leave your review and an image, I love to see what you can do with the models!! have fun.”

CHECK THE OTHER LORAS!!!
